{"tid":1287544,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［迷因］一人一個好笑的meme","createTime":"2019-07-05T08:59:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T09:34:19.000Z","uid":194789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"516c19d92029253c6f83aad6f549d8e04336a4da","tid":1287544,"uid":194789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:59:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7YeHqtDTSeY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7YeHqtDTSeY&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BIE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=86406790\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7YeHqtDTSeY</a><br />\n<br />\n首先翻開隨處可見的字典，可以看到meme的解釋有兩個。<br />\n<br />\n 第一個：「在某個文化中，從一個人傳播到另一個人的想法，行為，風格或用法。」<br />\n它是指某樣東西被模仿、再造、傳遞。而所謂的「東西」，並不一定是實體的，也有可能是一個想法，或是一段旋律。<br />\n<br />\n第二個解釋：「一個有趣的東西（如加上字幕的圖片或影片）或一個在網路上（特別是社交媒體上）被廣泛轉載的東西。」這個聽起來比較接近一般公認meme的意思。<br />\n<br />\nmeme必須「有趣」；再來，它必須在「網路或社交媒體」被「瘋狂轉載」。我們可以說meme就是在網路上的「爆紅事物」，仔細看看維基百科的「網路爆紅列表」，可以看見許多熟悉的meme名列其中，像彩虹貓<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n純粹我想睇memes<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />為生活調下味"},{"pid":"4a50810d80dc9110a5530b18531244a03551fcd1","tid":1287544,"uid":164190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:22:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/rXa3WJOUdjs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FrXa3WJOUdjs&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BIE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=5403974d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/rXa3WJOUdjs</a>"},{"pid":"1086353e5bf653f0eb3e2ea251804e1775f53325","tid":1287544,"uid":164190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:25:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/eEjNkXAZVdk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FeEjNkXAZVdk&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BIE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=13aad27b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/eEjNkXAZVdk</a>"},{"pid":"50d02f5a44a7e157405b51566b601ca871f44cef","tid":1287544,"uid":194789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:27:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b66b047f31ebfe8cd2099d2250e682fc228772fd","tid":1287544,"uid":194789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:27:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"caf2c3074a3357cf3d76dc2527e9706f886143f8","tid":1287544,"uid":194789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:27:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1cb9449227d4dc63c05b9fc4003125c49b304833","tid":1287544,"uid":194789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:27:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"86b5b45c7a27954c4a92ec1054c0504866c693ab","tid":1287544,"uid":194789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:28:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"84f9266abf619ece518947bdb810a214ae32b2bb","tid":1287544,"uid":164190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:34:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ht28eSuksIQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fht28eSuksIQ&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BIE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=3293755a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ht28eSuksIQ</a>"}]}